                                Jaschke, A. C., ArtEZ Univ Arts, Dept Mus Therapy, Enschede, Netherlands.
                                Jaschke, A. C., Univ Med Ctr Groningen, Beatrix Childrens Hosp, Dept Neonatol, Groningen, Netherlands.
                                Howlin, C., Trinity Coll Dublin, Dept Psychol, Dublin, Ireland.
